Privacy Policy
Introduction

This Privacy Policy explains what information FitCoach collects, how we use it, and the choices you have.
FitCoach is a fitness app designed for personal users and fitness trainers. This SERVICE is provided at no cost and intended for use as is.
By using FitCoach, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy. The personal information we collect is used to provide and improve the Service. We will not share your information with third parties except as described in this Privacy Policy.

Information Collection and Use
To ensure proper functionality and provide a personalized experience, FitCoach collects certain information from users, including but not limited to:
Name, email address, and optional profile pictures
Fitness-related data: workouts, exercises, nutrition logs, progress measurements, and photos
Device information and usage statistics
All collected data is stored securely in encrypted form using Firebase. This data is used only to provide the app’s features, improve user experience, and prevent abuse or fraud. Third parties do not have access to your personal information.

Cookies
FitCoach does not use cookies explicitly. Some third-party libraries integrated into the app may use cookies or similar technologies to collect information to improve their services. You may choose to accept or refuse cookies, but certain features of the Service may not function properly if cookies are disabled.

Location Information
Some features may use location information from your device (e.g., searching for nearby trainers). We only use this data within the scope necessary to provide these services.

Device Information
FitCoach may collect certain device information, such as model, OS version, and app usage statistics. This information helps improve app performance and stability. It does not include personally identifiable information unless explicitly provided by you.

Service Providers
We may employ trusted third-party providers to support the app’s functionality, including analytics and cloud storage. These providers have access only to the data required to perform their tasks and are obligated not to use it for other purposes.

Security
FitCoach takes the security of your personal information seriously. We use commercially reasonable measures to protect your data, including encryption and secure storage. However, no method of electronic transmission or storage is completely secure.

Delete Account
You can request deletion of your account and associated data through the “Delete Account” option in the app. Once requested, all personal information, fitness logs, and uploaded media will be permanently deleted. Account recovery is not possible after deletion.

Children’s Privacy
FitCoach does not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we become aware that a child under 13 has provided personal data, it will be promptly deleted. Parents or guardians can contact us to ensure necessary actions are taken.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. You are encouraged to review it regularly. Changes take effect immediately upon posting.

Contact Us
For any questions or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or your personal data, please contact:
Email: urvandimon@gmail.com
